title: Large House for 9/1, HW Floors, Updated Kitchen, 2 Baths, Garage
posting_body: ['Large House next to St. Thomas for 9/1, HW Floors, Updated Kitchen, Sunroom, Yard Space, 2 Car Garage', 'Property Address', '2070 Goodrich Ave | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'Large house next to St. Thomas available September 1.', ' The main level has hardwood floors throughout.', " There's a living room between the sunroom and full dining room.", " Kitchen has stainless steel appliances, and there's a new kitchen floor being installed.", ' There are 3 bedrooms upstairs with a full bathroom in between.', ' One of the bedrooms has a sunroom attached to it.', ' Two more bedrooms downstairs with a 3/4 bathroom and washer/dryer.', "There's yard space, a back patio, and 2 car detached garage with automatic openers.", ' Fantastic St. Paul location just two blocks from the University of St. Thomas campus.', 'Rent includes water, trash & lawn care', 'Two smalls pets are okay with a $50/month pet fee per', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a showing', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 5BD/2.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,800', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $3,200.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $3,200.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Small dogs allowed']
